At Five Star Painting, we understand the importance of color. From a fresh exterior paint job that improves the curb appeal of your home or business, to interior paint that brings style and feeling to your daily life, paint can make all the difference. profile: We are a painting company in business for over 15 years we do Residential and Commercial painting ,from custom homes to commercial buildings we do it all , We have all 5 star google reviews ,feel free to check us out on social media, We have 2 million liability insurance and we are WSIB Compliant. Areas we serve are Niagara Falls and area, St Cathrines, Vineland, Beamsville, Grimsby, Stoney Creek, Hamilton, Ancaster, Burlington, Dundas. Why Choose Peninsula Painting Contractors ,We treat your home or business like it’s ours. This means using only the best quality painting products and services for each project. Our painting contractors go above and beyond to ensure your local painting service is a delightful experience from start to finish. We select the highest performing paints, primers and repair materials that will leave your space looking beautiful for years to come. Our experience in interior and exterior painting projects paired with Peninsula’s streamlined booking process puts us ahead of other painters in the region. Whether you require Peninsula Painting for residential or commercial painting projects, our painting professionals are there with you every step of the way to answer your questions before, during and after your project has been completed .Our Commitment to Customers, At Peninsula Painting, we stand by the work we do, as it’s our mission to provide the highest quality of craftsmanship with unparalleled customer support, reliability and integrity. We specialize in interior and exterior painting for residential and commercial jobs so you can feel confident that you’ll always love your home or business's new look! Contact us today for a free quote.
